702
01:06:28,440 --> 01:06:33,036
Well, you know, I've always wanted
to go to New Orleans.

703
01:06:33,560 --> 01:06:36,233
New Orleans. Why New Orleans?

704
01:06:36,840 --> 01:06:38,273
Bourbon St.

705
01:06:40,040 --> 01:06:41,553
